name: The Three Musketeers
description: This photo is clicked from Bangalore, Karnataka, India. The beautiful tree with sunset in background was a sight to remember, However the birds are from metaverse! This is an experimental artificial photographic idea. This photo was clicked in 2018 using a Canon EOS 600D and 50mm lens. This work is my solidarity to HENXMAS theme for H=N in July & celebration of hicetnunc2000 community. I hope the three friends chilling on a tree brings the idea of Christmas spirit in July :) Resolution - 1558*1948
